{"tid":1051357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解女權撚咁乞人憎","createTime":"2019-03-07T14:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T15:12:18.000Z","uid":237709,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1d6225cbfb2f0c5c043139b3890ab3c6730f26","tid":1051357,"uid":237709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"曾幾何時<br />\n女權主義嘅誔生<br />\n係因為當時女性生處喺極端父系社會<br />\n基本談唔上有任何權利<br />\n因此女權嘅初衷係為女性們爭取多啲權益<br />\n令女性們有返基本嘅權利<br />\n<br />\n既然女權主義嘅出發點係好<br />\n咁點解咁多人咁憎女權呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為現今嘅女權主義唔再係昔日嘅女權主義<br />\n現今嘅女權主義<br />\n只可以用兩隻字形容<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">虛偽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-lK-SdaQL3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-lK-SdaQL3A&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=6c62df52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-lK-SdaQL3A</a><br />\n以上片段講得好清楚<br />\n宜家嘅女權已經超出咗為女人爭取嘅地步<br />\n佢哋仲會為黑人、lgbt、肥撚等「弱勢族群」爭取<br />\n而且特別針對白種男人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n齋用文字表達好似唔夠具體<br />\n所以我擺咗啲女權撚嘅例子出嚟<br />\n畀大家睇吓究竟班女權撚有幾乞人憎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 女權撚：婚姻係反平權嘅行為<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRYzl6o0xks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRYzl6o0xks&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=fe3ca7c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRYzl6o0xks</a><br />\n片中嘅人表示婚姻=向男士低頭<br />\n所以係有違平權<br />\n<br />\n2. 女權撚認為只有男人先可以企喺到屙尿係違反平權<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0AKeRiGK4uY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0AKeRiGK4uY&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=a00a4526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0AKeRiGK4uY</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9OaKhZ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9OaKhZ1.png&h=9deb21ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://presentationvoice.com/all-posts/opinions/2018/05/18/feminism-at-its-finest-peeing-standing-up/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpresentationvoice.com%2Fall-posts%2Fopinions%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2Ffeminism-at-its-finest-peeing-standing-up%2F&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=64c85eaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://presentationvoice.com/all-posts/opinions/2018/05/18/feminism-at-its-finest-peeing-standing-up/</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 女權撚最鍾意Victimize自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jmeTnVywvwU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjmeTnVywvwU&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=9aa80374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jmeTnVywvwU</a><br />\n好似呢條片咁，女權撚自創Mansplaining一字，意指男人過度向女人解釋嘅現象，並認為呢啲係要斟酌嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NQglZPVmoo8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNQglZPVmoo8&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=3c78adad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NQglZPVmoo8</a><br />\n女權撚又自創詞彙，將男人擘開雙腿嚟坐嘅現象叫做Manspreading。前排仲要有個俄國女權撚用漂白水撥向喺地鐵內&rdquo;Manspreading&rdquo;嘅人<br />\n<br />\n4. 女權撚認為唔應該叫女人做girl<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/apvnjXvRovk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FapvnjXvRovk&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQurkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=5a6df098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/apvnjXvRovk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想贈班女權一句<br />\nSTOP CREATING PROBLEMS THAT DONT EXIST"},{"pid":"1d51f8ed266beb0d4984ea62b8f765ef37ddb7cf","tid":1051357,"uid":237709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T14:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbe5b85c5547649965cc306413efe4ec8d1cb36","tid":1051357,"uid":124491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"十卜女權撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4440a1b07d25e73ad85b5e0